data.description: SELLER OFFERING $13K Seller Credit for 2/1 Buydown rate as low as 4.5% ASK FOR DETAILS!! Fantastic like-new home in highly desired Thompson Crossing subdivision. Guests are greeted by a formal entry flowing into open floor plan with dramatic vaulted ceilings This 3 Bed 3 Bath home feels open and light, featuring hardwood floors, 42" soft close cabinets, crown molding, hand trowel drywall finish, a gas fireplace, and 2 hot water heaters. Ensuite 5-piece master with spacious walk-in closet. Enjoy mountain views in the loft and backyard. Adjacent to great retail at Johnstown Plaza and Centerra only a minute away.  No Metro Tax!
